        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_diagram.jpg", "text": "Start:  Start with a chain using an odd number of stitches. Stitch multiple is 2 + 3. Each “feather” is the width of two chains.  The CH-1 at the beginning of the row does NOT count as a stitch. "},
        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step1and2.jpg", "text": "Step 1:  1. Chain an odd number of stitches. Half double crochet in the third chain from the hook. "},
