        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step3.jpg", "text": "Step 3: To start the next row, chain one and turn. Half double crochet in the first stitch, and then chain one. "},
        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step4.PNG", "text": "Step 4:  To make a feather stitch: * Yarn over pull up a loop in the chain-space. (3 loops on hook)  "},
