        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step4_4.PNG", "text": " (7 loops on hook) Yarn over and pull through all 7 loops.  "},
        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step4_5.PNG", "text": "Chain one to close the stitch. Feather stitch made! "},
        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step5.PNG", "text": "Step 5: 5. Repeat step 4 to the end of the row. When you get there, half double crochet in the last stitch. (don’t forget the chain one to close the final feather) "},
        {"image": "assets/feather/feather_step5_1.PNG", "text": "Step 5: 5. Repeat step 4 to the end of the row. When you get there, half double crochet in the last stitch. (don’t forget the chain one to close the final feather) "},
